    "If the relevant part of the input is discarded this will lead to false predictions.",
    "To address this issue we need a way to process longer input sequences.",
    "Several approaches are available:",
    "(a) Applying the limited-length model to chunks of the text sequences.",
    "(b) Using a model which can handle more than 512 tokens."
